4,511,394],{"class":64},[54,513,514],{"class":68},"()\n",[16,516,517,518,520,521,523],{},"在這邊這一段程式碼 ",[51,519,414],{}," 是建立於 ",[51,522,394],{}," 中，因此當程式碼執行完畢時，他會釋放掉記憶體也就是 Garbage collection，但是你會發現記憶體還是佔用 9.3 MB",[16,525,526],{},[26,527],{"alt":420,"src":421},[16,529,530,531,533],{},"這時候你可能會想說「變數不是建立在 ",[51,532,394],{}," 嗎？那麼應該會被釋放記憶體呀？」，沒有錯，但記憶體會這樣佔用的原因主要是 console 也會暫用記憶體空間，因此你只需要將 console 清空(不是 Reset) 就會發現記憶體變成 4.3 MB",[16,535,536],{},[26,537],{"alt":538,"src":539},"Console 佔用","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002FJavaScript%20%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E8%A7%80%E5%BF%B5\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-05-24%2016.14.14.png",[12,541,542],{"id":542},"參考文獻",[544,545,546,556],"ul",{},[547,548,549],"li",{},[550,551,555],"a",{"href":552,"rel":553},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.hexschool.com\u002Fcourses\u002Fjs-core.html",[554],"nofollow","六角學院 - JavaScript 核心篇",[547,557,558],{},[550,559,562],{"href":560,"rel":561},"https:\u002F\u002Fdeveloper.mozilla.org\u002Fzh-TW\u002Fdocs\u002FWeb\u002FJavaScript\u002FMemory_Management",[554],"記憶體管理",[564,565,566],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sOudu, html code.shiki .sOudu{--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-default:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#FF9492}html pre.shiki code .scAaK, html code.shiki .scAaK{--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-default:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DBB7FF}html pre.shiki code .s8XSl, html code.shiki .s8XSl{--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-default:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sGBqm, html code.shiki .sGBqm{--shiki-light:#6A737D;--shiki-default:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#BDC4CC}html .light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html.light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light